title: Degree of urbanization in Australia 2018
yAxis: Share of urban population in total population
summary: Overall Share of urban population in total population has increased over the Year.
Share of urban population in total population is slightly increasing from 2014 to 2018.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2017 and 2018.
Maximum Share of urban population in total population, about 86.01 was reported at Year 2018
Minimum Share of urban population in total population about 85.6 was reached at Year 2014
